Patch 8.0.0067
Problem:    VMS has a problem with infinity.
Solution:   Avoid an overflow. (Zoltan Arpadffy)
Files:      src/json.c, src/macros.h


*** ../vim-8.0.0066/src/json.c	2016-11-04 20:35:27.348946021 +0100
